item.title: SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_Common
item.description: SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_Common Datatype Description The SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_Common data type contains common information for responses from the getPortalLogin API. This is an abstract class that serves as a base that more specialized classes will derive from. For example, a response class that is specific to a successful response from the getPortalLogin API. Local accounts The list of linked accounts for the authenticated SoftLayer customer portal user. Type: SoftLayer_Container_Authentication_Response_Account[]
